summary:
During my experience as a teacher I have always tried to get the best from every pupil. I look for progress and I believe in a global development that will help students to become critical citizens. 

In Spain I have worked with pupils from 3 till 18 years old as a private English, Spanish, Science and Maths tutor, and I also have experience from 3 periods of training at a Primary School, while I was studying my degree. During the academic year 2015/2016 I worked in England as a Spanish Assistant at the Secondary school Sanders School, where I also supported the French teacher occasionally. 

Since 2016 I am working at Pasaréti Gimnázium, a high school in Budapest, where I teach English and Spanish.
